{"tid":2132503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 中華民國前總統李登輝 於30日晚上7時24分病逝，享壽95歲","createTime":"2020-07-30T12:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T12:49:35.000Z","uid":52658,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"50e33c40f209ee524bb11849f75fcfa9b4c6d9df","tid":2132503,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"台北榮總今（30）日證實，李前總統已在晚間19點24分病逝，享耆壽98歲。院方將在晚間出 面說明，並表示李前總統的大體會先暫存在醫院，待家屬做後續安排。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝前年跌倒就醫後，就鮮少在公開場合露面，最後一次露面是總統蔡英文在今年1月14 日剛勝選後，在總統府秘書長陳菊陪同下，一同到李登輝官邸拜訪，提前祝壽。之後就因嗆 到引發吸入性肺炎後，住進台北榮總治療，屢次傳出過世消息，辦公室主任王燕軍也多次出 面澄清死訊。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝在今年2月8日因為喝牛奶嗆到引發吸入性肺炎，之後還出現持續發炎且頻繁發燒，肺 積水無法完全排除，僅能以抗生素控制，多處於昏睡狀態，一直住在北榮中正樓22樓的總統 病房，之後北榮和主治醫師也封口不談病情。<br />\n<br />\n李總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />R.I.P<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1596110373.A.94D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1596110373.A.94D.html&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=7ae4490d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1596110373.A.94D.html</a>"},{"pid":"e27fbead6bddc0d4219a893ec08ef8735eaf9b01","tid":2132503,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"李總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd898f383110fe67debe36b348f78cd44b20056","tid":2132503,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"歹勢 錯標題 享壽98歲"},{"pid":"6f5d52f7842e615ab6fedbefe3b0d015bb87a18d","tid":2132503,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img